{"tid":2163103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去留之爭唯一解方：請初選勝出者盡快召開會議決定去留對策","createTime":"2020-08-18T12:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T14:34:08.000Z","uid":109462,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fb5b310d568fd6f96f8e181067c1b44c03e10148","tid":2163103,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:55:14.000Z","msg":"去留之爭去到今日，兩邊嘅論點其實已經陳述曬，本地同外國嘅學者亦都已經表達過意見，係時候召開初選勝出者會議去決定到底應該點樣做。<br />\n<br />\n去留之爭呢件大事，自然無可能單單由一黨一派自己決定；但公投亦非完美，一來費時失事，二來責任分散，好似英國脫歐咁，萬一最後嘅結果令大家追悔莫及，都無人需要承擔責任。<br />\n<br />\n因此由初選勝出者召開會議，直播辯論、記名表決，就係最好嘅解方。<br />\n<br />\n從民意授權論：初選勝出者本身就有最新嘅民意授權，所以民意基礎方面一定比泛民「飯盒會」自己決定來得高。<br />\n從公平性論：初選勝出者包含泛民同抗爭派，一齊開會決定，就可以避免有人話個會偏袒某一方。<br />\n從效率論：初選勝出者幾十人聚埋一齊開會決定，點睇都比搞公投快，唔會夜長夢多。<br />\n從責任論：直播辯論、記名表決，可以留低歷史紀錄，最後結果無論成敗，功過毀譽都有所歸，唔使好似英國脫歐咁樣責任分散而到最後無人需要負責。<br />\n<br />\n請初選勝出者盡快召開會議決定去留對策，有決定之後就請大家捐棄前嫌、同心遵從，避免陷入無止境嘅爭論與撕裂。"},{"pid":"eb3ee1c683582eed34d0f19fe2e6ff8c616e1ea4","tid":2163103,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:57:23.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c27d3110d14604fc7c113b01f8afcc3d1ccf8de","tid":2163103,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:59:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a99dc5ab8ac8a24ad0c5b745976fe21153a10e","tid":2163103,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:02:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f8c5bea7848f252c86af184434b162093710e5","tid":2163103,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:03:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3073c214adc286597c9c268c694b067f9766c757","tid":2163103,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:05:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daae42cf2be3bc53dfafff2079671c9d53d86795","tid":2163103,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:12:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da10ee5ba34d5c2c5ece83b7a18ce25fb6a9814","tid":2163103,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:41:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d285beecf62aa7817e6b5e3fc39fde045d4a9a05","tid":2163103,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:15:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc263f7ac41c5e96488ff9ae7a269a1aa732778e","tid":2163103,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:22:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0dcb609927a6e14412511fd9f9ab83a40722b1","tid":2163103,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee9de497866ff05a23aa5e1a26361baadb755b3","tid":2163103,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:34:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}